### Important Guidelines

- Group related templates into logical features (e.g., "product-tile" includes template + JS + styles)
- Assign priority based on user visibility and business impact (1 = highest)
- Mark migrationComplexity based on jQuery/Bootstrap usage density
- Include ALL jQuery patterns found, even seemingly simple ones
- Document inter-feature dependencies to determine migration order
